.\" Man page for gghstats(1)
.TH GGHSTATS 1 "May 2026" "gghstats" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
gghstats \- self-hosted GitHub repository traffic dashboard and CLI
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B gghstats
.I command
.RB [ flags ]
.PP
.B gghstats serve
.RB [ \-\-port
.IR PORT ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B gghstats
collects GitHub traffic metrics (views, clones, referrers, paths) into a local
SQLite database so history is kept beyond GitHub's 14-day window. It can run as
a web dashboard with scheduled sync, or as CLI commands for fetch, report, and
export.
.PP
Server mode (\fBserve\fR) requires a GitHub personal access token with access to
the repositories you want to track.
.PP
Configuration uses environment variables (prefix
.BR GGHSTATS_ ).
On Linux servers under systemd, set them in
.IR /etc/gghstats/gghstats.env
(see
.IR contrib/gghstats.env.example ).
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B serve
Start the HTTP dashboard and background sync scheduler.
.TP
.B fetch
Download traffic for one repository into the database.
.TP
.B report
Print a traffic summary in the terminal.
.TP
.B export
Export traffic data to CSV.
.TP
.B version
Print build version information.
.SH CLI FLAGS
(fetch, report, export)
.TP
.BR \-\-repo ", " owner/repo
Repository (or \fBGGHSTATS_REPO\fR).
.TP
.BR \-\-token ", " TOKEN
GitHub token (or \fBGGHSTATS_GITHUB_TOKEN\fR).
.TP
.BR \-\-db ", " PATH
SQLite database path (default: \fB./data/gghstats.db\fR).
.SH SERVE FLAGS
.TP
.BR \-\-port ", " PORT
Listen port (overrides \fBGGHSTATS_PORT\fR; default \fB8080\fR).
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B GGHSTATS_GITHUB_TOKEN
GitHub personal access token (required for \fBserve\fR).
.TP
.B GGHSTATS_DB
SQLite path (default: \fB./data/gghstats.db\fR).
.TP
.B GGHSTATS_HOST
Bind address (default: \fB127.0.0.1\fR; use \fB0.0.0.0\fR in Docker).
.TP
.B GGHSTATS_PORT
Listen port (default: \fB8080\fR).
.TP
.B GGHSTATS_FILTER
Repository filter (default: \fB*\fR = all accessible).
.TP
.B GGHSTATS_SYNC_INTERVAL
Sync frequency (default: \fB1h\fR).
.TP
.B GGHSTATS_SYNC_ON_STARTUP
Run sync before serving (default: \fBtrue\fR).
.TP
.B GGHSTATS_API_TOKEN
Protect JSON API routes; optional for manual sync from the UI.
.TP
.B GGHSTATS_BADGE_PUBLIC
Allow public badge SVG URLs (default: \fBtrue\fR).
.TP
.B GGHSTATS_LOG_LEVEL
\fBdebug\fR, \fBinfo\fR (default), \fBwarn\fR, or \fBerror\fR.
.TP
.B GGHSTATS_METRICS
Set to \fBfalse\fR to disable Prometheus \fB/metrics\fR.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
Run the dashboard locally:
.RS
.EX
export GGHSTATS_GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_xxx
gghstats serve
.EE
Open \fIhttp://localhost:8080\fR.
.RE
.TP
Fetch one repository:
.RS
.EX
gghstats fetch --repo owner/repo --token "$GGHSTATS_GITHUB_TOKEN"
.EE
.RE
.SH FILES
.IR /etc/gghstats/gghstats.env
Environment file for systemd (\fBserve\fR). Installed by .deb/.rpm; see
.IR contrib/gghstats.env.example .
.PP
systemd unit:
.IR contrib/systemd/gghstats.service
(see
.IR contrib/systemd/README.md ).
.SH EXIT STATUS
0 on success, non-zero on error.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR https://github.com/hrodrig/gghstats
.SH AUTHOR
Hermes Rodriguez
